{"tid":1655933,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拒絕巴塞隆拿邀請 連迪路夫想為曼聯捧盃","createTime":"2019-10-15T10:23:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T14:47:40.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ea864795adf8472b2733d5cc519a4c57fbf7a909","tid":1655933,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:23:46.000Z","msg":"曼聯今季成績令人失望，陣中球員表現被受批評，不過瑞典後衛連迪路夫沒有因此而心灰意冷，他接受傳媒訪問時透露，自己拒絕了巴塞隆拿的邀請，希望留效曼聯贏得冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n今個夏天有傳巴塞隆拿向他招手，這位大將表示自己從來沒有想過離開曼聯，又指留下來的原因是因為深愛球隊，希望能為球隊贏得錦標。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n連迪路夫又認為自己有領導才能，並會為隊友發聲，勝任曼聯隊友一職。上月曼聯宣佈與連迪路夫至 2024 年，周薪高達 15 萬鎊。<br />\n<br />\n網上圖片"},{"pid":"f75444dff4374a34ec318e0b60732b7b8d0099dc","tid":1655933,"uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:23:55.000Z","msg":"忠心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9dcf93c6e009b92c1a4627e46ab84405c61164","tid":1655933,"uid":3747,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"想捧盃咁你又漏頂"},{"pid":"14abd06519cb327e160c47c25e59d8fbe8157966","tid":1655933,"uid":75046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2910ec9df98496fc5b513611367a728e508f3f21","tid":1655933,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"英冠獎盃都係盃"},{"pid":"f9d6f9028706d41044ebe450690717c2776e0e0e","tid":1655933,"uid":31173,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"巴塞想買佢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔撚係掛"},{"pid":"de551539e4958c8e34d6983219f25bc805bc0de8","tid":1655933,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9d6f9028706d41044ebe450690717c2776e0e0e","tid":1655933,"uid":31173,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"